snippet.title: Atomic Picnic - Official Trailer | Future of Play Direct 2023
snippet.description:
See gameplay, characters, and more in this trailer for Atomic Picnic, an upcoming 4-Player co-op shooter roguelite game. In Atomic Picnic, get together with up to 4 friends, defeat hordes of monsters, and upgrade your powers to survive in an anime-style wasteland.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
